```
nAry 1 ℕ ℕ
≡ (fun n A B ↦ Nat.rec B (fun k nAry_k ↦ A → nAry_k) n) 1 ℕ ℕ
≡ Nat.rec ℕ (fun k nAry_k ↦ ℕ → nAry_k) 1
≡ ℕ → Nat.rec ℕ (fun k nAry_k ↦ ℕ → nAry_k) 0
≡ ℕ → ℕ
```
where the steps are respectively
- δ-reduction
- 3 times β-reduction
- η-reduction (plus twice β-reduction)
- η-reduction
